'''若热·-{桑}-帕約'''，澳門譯為'''-{沈}-拜奧'''（{{lang-pt|'''Jorge Fernando Branco de Sampaio'''}}；{{bd|1939年|9月18日|2021年|9月10日|catIdx=Sampaio}}<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-09-10|title=Jorge Sampaio, who showed extent of Portuguese presidential powers, dies at 81|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|url=https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/jorge-sampaio-who-showed-teeth-portuguese-presidential-powers-dies-81-2021-09-10/|accessdate=2021-09-11|archive-date=2021-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029103641/https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/jorge-sampaio-who-showed-teeth-portuguese-presidential-powers-dies-81-2021-09-10/|dead-url=no}}</ref>），[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[社會黨_(葡萄牙)|社會黨]]政治人物。是[[康乃馨革命|葡萄牙康乃馨革命]]后第五任[[葡萄牙總統|葡萄牙總統]]，1996年3月9日當選，2001年獲得連任，2013年卸任退休。

2021年9月10日，沈拜奧因呼吸系統衰竭於里斯本聖克魯斯醫院（Hospital de Santa Cruz）逝世<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-09-10|title=Morreu Jorge Sampaio, o "prisioneiro da ansiedade por um futuro melhor"|publisher=Jornal de Notícias|url=https://www.jn.pt/nacional/morreu-jorge-sampaio-o-prisioneiro-da-ansiedade-por-um-futuro-melhor-14082235.html/|accessdate=2021-09-11|archive-date=2021-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210911120915/https://www.jn.pt/nacional/morreu-jorge-sampaio-o-prisioneiro-da-ansiedade-por-um-futuro-melhor-14082235.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，時任澳門行政長官[[賀一誠|賀一誠]]發出唁函<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-09-13|title=行政長官深切悼念葡萄牙前總統若熱．桑帕約|publisher=澳門新聞局|url=https://www.gcs.gov.mo/detail/zh-hant/N21IMmNXdX|accessdate=2021-09-13}}</ref>，並委派[[澳門駐里斯本經濟貿易辦事處|澳門駐里斯本經濟貿易辦事處]]主任[[譚俊榮|譚俊榮]]代表特區政府出席9月12日的國葬儀式<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-09-13|title=特區政府委派澳門駐里斯本經貿辦事處代表出席葡萄牙前總統若熱．桑帕約國葬儀式|url=https://www.gcs.gov.mo/detail/zh-hant/N21IMCuD2g|accessdate=2021-09-13}}</ref>；中华人民共和国国家主席[[习近平|习近平]]9月12日致唁电，稱桑帕约為葡萄牙杰出的政治家和领导人，在国际社会享有很高声誉<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-09-13|title=习近平就葡萄牙前总统桑帕约逝世向葡萄牙总统德索萨致唁电|url=http://www.news.cn/2021-09/13/c_1127857091.htm|accessdate=2021-09-13|archive-date=2021-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210913134001/http://www.news.cn/2021-09/13/c_1127857091.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 早年的生活和政治生涯 ==
桑帕约生于里斯本。桑帕约一家在美国和英国生活了几年，这是由于他的父亲Arnaldo de Sampaio(1908-1984)的职业活动，他父亲是一名医生。他的母亲是Fernanda Bensaude Branco(1908 - 2000年2月15日)。他的外祖母Sara Bensliman Bensaude于1976年去世，是来自摩洛哥的葡萄牙血统的西班牙系犹太人，外祖父Fernando Branco(1880-1940)是葡萄牙海军军官，后来担任葡萄牙外交部长；桑帕约自己是不可知论者，并不认为自己是犹太人。<ref>See [http://www.shavei.org/communities/bnei_anousim/articles-bnei_anousim/portugal%C2%B4s-president-%C2%B4i-am-proud-of-my-jewish-ancestry%C2%B4/?lang=en Portugal´s President: ´I am proud of my Jewish ancestry´] {{Wayback|url=http://www.shavei.org/communities/bnei_anousim/articles-bnei_anousim/portugal%C2%B4s-president-%C2%B4i-am-proud-of-my-jewish-ancestry%C2%B4/?lang=en |date=20150924101132 }}, Michael Freund, retrieved from the [https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/jpost/access/443340731.html?dids=443340731:443340731&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Nov+7%2C+2003&author=MICHAEL+FREUND&pub=Jerusalem+Post&edition=&startpage=06&desc=Portugal%27s+president%3A+%27I+am+proud+of+my+Jewish+ancestry%27 Jerusalem Post of 7 November 2003] {{Wayback|url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/jpost/access/443340731.html?dids=443340731:443340731&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Nov+7%2C+2003&author=MICHAEL+FREUND&pub=Jerusalem+Post&edition=&startpage=06&desc=Portugal%27s+president%3A+%27I+am+proud+of+my+Jewish+ancestry%27 |date=20080209185024 }}:   
<blockquote>Jerusalem Post: I understand that you have Jewish ancestry in your family. What is your personal connection to the Jewish people? Do you consider yourself to be a Jew?.</blockquote>   
<blockquote>Jorge Sampaio: My grandmother belonged to a Jewish family that came from Morocco in the beginning of the 19th century. She married a non-Jewish naval officer who later was Foreign Affairs minister. I am naturally very proud of this ancestry and of all those that I call my "favorite Jewish cousins," one of whom is the president of the Lisbon Jewish Community, as I am proud of the ancestry on my non-Jewish father's side. Personally, I am agnostic, and I do not consider myself a Jew; but I am proud, as I said, of my ancestors.</blockquote></ref> 

他小时候在里斯本的美国学校上学。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.publico.pt/2010/07/26/sociedade/noticia/encontro-de-irmaos-1448767 |title=Publico - Daniel e Jorge Sampaio: Encontro de Irmãos |accessdate=2020-05-18 |archive-date=2020-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329045233/https://www.publico.pt/2010/07/26/sociedade/noticia/encontro-de-irmaos-1448767 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>他的政治生涯始于里斯本大学法学院的学生时代。桑帕约参与学生反对法西斯政权的辩论，并在1960年至1961年期间担任里斯本学生会主席。1961年毕业后，桑帕约开始了著名的律师生涯，曾为许多政治犯辩护。

